24/09/babyshambles@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/babyshambles@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/babyshambles@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/babyshambles@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>国家专辑日 (NAD) 宣布今年回归，一系列限量经典黑胶唱片将重新发行，其中包括英国最伟大的一些表演 - 请参阅下面的完整列表。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/cd-revival-2022-punk-vinyl-cassette-3155194">CD 复兴？它可能会成为最朋克的音乐格式</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的国家专辑日将于10月19日举行，主题为“伟大的英国组合”。今年，该活动与官方广播合作伙伴<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bbc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC Radio 2</em></a>联合举办。作为今年庆祝活动的一部分，NAD <a href="https://www.nationalalbumday.co.uk/news/national-album-day-announces-lineup-of-exclusive-releases-reissues-from-british-groups-to-coincide-with-annual-event-on-saturday-19th-october/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宣布将重新发行 40 多张经典黑胶唱片</a>。</p><p>所有这些特殊专辑都可以在英国各地的零售商处以及<a href="https://www.nationalalbumday.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">通过 NAD 本身</a>购买——大量此类唱片将从英国夏令时今天上午 10 点（9 月 12 日）开始接受预订。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792918" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792918" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792918" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/idlewild-warnings-promises-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792918" class="wp-caption-text">艾德维尔德的“警告/承诺”。图片来源：全国专辑日</figcaption></figure><p>今天推出的作品包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babyshambles">Babyshambles</a>的“Shotter&#39;s Nation”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idlewild">Idlewild</a>的“Warnings/Promises”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a>的“British Steel”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daughter">Daughter</a>的“Music From Before The Storm”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-minds">Simple Minds</a>的“Big Music”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slowdive">Slowdive</a>的同名唱片、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/t-rex">T. Rex</a>的《The Slider》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-proclaimers">The Proclaimers</a>的《This Is The Story》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/suede">Suede</a>的《Dog Man Star》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">Travis</a>的《The Man Who》等等。</p><h3><strong>今天晚些时候（9 月 12 日）可供预订的记录是：</strong></h3><p><strong>诸圣——‘诸圣’</strong><br /> <strong>Babyshambles – “射击者的国度”</strong><br /><strong>女儿——《暴风雨前的音乐》</strong><br /> <strong>Dodgy – “本土”</strong><br /><strong>拥抱——“无中生有”</strong><br /><strong>戈麦斯 – “我们如何运作”</strong><br /><strong>艾德维尔德——“警告/承诺”</strong><br /><strong>杰夫·韦恩 – “杰夫·韦恩的世界大战音乐版：ULLAdubULLA – 混音专辑”</strong><br /><strong>犹大牧师——“英国钢铁”</strong><br /> <strong>Longpigs – “太阳经常出来”</strong><br /><strong>迈克和机械师 – “Living Years”</strong><br /> <strong>Oysterband 和 June Tabor – 《自由与雨》</strong><br /> <strong>Prefab Sprout – 《乔丹：回归》</strong><br /><strong>女童子军——“女童子军”</strong><br /><strong>小屋——“英国皇家海军寓言”</strong><br /><strong>头脑简单——“大音乐”</strong><br /><strong>简单的红色——“简化”</strong><br /><strong>慢速潜水-“慢速潜水”</strong><br /><strong>麂皮绒——“狗人明星”</strong><br /> <strong>T. REX – “滑块”</strong><br /><strong>就这样——“一切都变了：30 周年”</strong><br /><strong>动物们——“动物们”</strong><br /><strong>化学兄弟 – “退出行星尘埃”</strong><br /><strong>秋天——“十六进制演绎时间”</strong><br /><strong>闪电种子 – &#39;Jollification&#39;</strong><br /><strong>宣告者——“这就是故事”</strong><br /><strong>慈悲修女会 – &#39;Floodland&#39;</strong><br /><strong>特别优惠——“特别优惠”</strong><br /><strong>绞杀者 – &#39;La Folie&#39;</strong><br /><strong>地铁 - &#39;金钱与名人&#39;（红白分离乙烯基）</strong><br /><strong>观点——“厚脸皮是有原因的”</strong><br /><strong>水男孩——“渔夫蓝调”</strong><br /><strong>特拉维斯——《神秘人》</strong><br /><strong>犹他圣徒队 – “犹他圣徒队”</strong><br /><strong>结婚礼物——“Bizarro”</strong><br /><strong>世界派对 – “再见 Jumbo”</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3792919" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792919" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792919" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/all-saints-all-saints-vinyl-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792919" class="wp-caption-text">诸圣’‘诸圣’。图片来源：全国专辑日</figcaption></figure><p>多张唱片也宣布将于英国夏令时 10 月 19 日上午 8 点开始发售。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/culture-club">文化俱乐部</a>的“Kissing To Be Clever”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Dire Straits</a>的“制作电影”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mumford-and-sons">Mumford &amp; Sons</a>的“Sigh No More”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>的“Angels With Dirty Faces”、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>的“