rrs 等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babyshambles-suede-all-saints-idlewild-and-more-to-reissue-limited-classic-lps-on-vinyl-for-national-album-day-2024-3792916">Babyshambles、Suede、All Saints、Idlewild 等乐队将在 2024 年国家专辑日重新发行限量经典黑胶唱片，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
